{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d41416522e","title":"关于三个世界划分问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"575bb330f5","index":0,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":22,"articleId":"d41416522e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji8","name":"毛泽东文集第八卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji8":{"comments":[{"id":"bddeeb1590","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":10,"text":"这是毛泽东同赞比亚总统卡翁达谈话的一部分。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a64e16ffaf","type":"title","text":"关于三个世界划分问题","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"bddeeb1590","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：希望第三世界团结起来。第三世界人口多啊！","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"9066b9f575","type":"paragraph","text":"卡翁达：对。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"86e2e74406","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：谁是第一世界？","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"ea3ec88b57","type":"paragraph","text":"卡：我想应该是那些剥削者和帝国主义者的世界。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"2452cb1667","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：第二世界呢？","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"a20489cd22","type":"paragraph","text":"卡：是那些已经变为修正主义分子的人。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"3c5830f011","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我看美国、苏联是第一世界。中间派，日本、欧洲、澳大利亚、加拿大，是第二世界。咱们是第三世界。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"f9a894a709","type":"paragraph","text":"卡：我同意主席先生的分析。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"6461250478","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：美国、苏联原子弹多，也比较富。第二世界，欧洲、日本、澳大利亚、加拿大，原子弹没有那么多，也没有那么富，但是比第三世界要富。你看这个解释好不好？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"66c1c53ed2","type":"paragraph","text":"卡：主席先生，你的分析很确切，十分准确。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"cb26b7dbc7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：研究一下吧。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"b535ca0962","type":"paragraph","text":"卡：我想不用研究，我们的意见就可以取得一致，因为在我看来，这个分析已经很确切了。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"74fe3e8c67","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：第三世界人口很多。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"ef5e0d462f","type":"paragraph","text":"卡：确实如此。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"bc63fc90e8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：亚洲除了日本，都是第三世界。整个非洲都是第三世界，拉丁美洲也是第三世界。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"c00575d358","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中央文献出版社、世界知识出版社","index":16,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"008a990493","type":"paragraph","text":"一九九四年出版的《毛泽东外交文选》","index":17,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"},{"id":"62f37c4933","type":"paragraph","text":"刊印。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e"}],"page":{"id":"594e2e7d93","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"d41416522e","start":452,"end":453}}}},"__N_SSG":true}